<p>	Q.  Do you find this to be a positive   -- I mean this could be on ESPN news; it could be picked you up by anybody every single week.  Is that a positive that you can reach this audience every week?</p>
<p>	Q.  This weekend not only is this team playing its first game this season but you are playing on a big stage, New York City, lots of media, lots of attention.  Are you at all concerned?  Are there concerns about young players who are not only playing new roles on the team, dealing with all of the hype -- it is unusual a little bit for the first game of the season?</p>
<p>	Q.  Are you doing anything along those lines heading into this weekend specifically?</p>
