<p>	Q.  A little bit about your philosophy of one of the things about getting through fall practice and not getting people too beat up or hurt.  Is there anything that you have noticed at Notre Dame that surprised you that you have had to change or is coaching coaching in terms of how you prepare your team and handle the team?</p>
